      "rationale": "Code verification performed via method of manufactured solutions (MMS) for the incompressible Navier-Stokes solver and the scalar transport equation used for hemolysis accumulation. Observed order of accuracy: 1.97 (spatial, second-order scheme confirmed) and 1.94 (temporal). Benchmark comparisons against ASME V&V 20 lid-driven cavity and backward-facing step cases demonstrate errors within 0.5% of reference solutions. Gradation 4 achieved.",
