      "rationale": "Quantitative output comparison performed for hemolysis index (NIH), pump pressure rise, and velocity field at all applicable operating points. Validation metric: E_rms computed per ASME V&V 20. NIH E_rms = 8.3% across 5 operating points. Pressure rise E_rms = 3.8%. Velocity field area-weighted RMS = 4.2%. Statistical comparison accounts for both experimental uncertainty and numerical uncertainty; all comparisons demonstrate model predictions within combined uncertainty bounds. Bayesian model validation metric confirms posterior probability of model adequacy > 0.95. Gradation 5 achieved, exceeding the Gradation 4 requirement.",
