      "rationale": "Model form selection justified through literature review of turbulence model performance for confined rotating flows (SST k-ω selected over realizable k-ε and RSM based on benchmark comparisons). Hemolysis sub-model (modified Giersiepen-Wurzinger power law) selected after comparison of four candidate models against the Arora mechanistic model and the Zhang correlation. Model form uncertainty quantified by running all five operating points with three turbulence model variants; NIH sensitivity to turbulence model: ±6% maximum. Documented model form uncertainty budget included in UQ ensemble. Gradation 4 achieved.",
