      "factorType": "Model inputs",
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "requiredLevel": 4,
      "achievedLevel": 4,
      "rationale": "All model input parameters characterized with probability distributions derived from experimental measurements or literature meta-analysis. Hemolysis model coefficients C and α calibrated against 12 independent in-vitro datasets; posterior distributions obtained via Bayesian inference (MCMC, 50 000 samples). Blood viscosity distribution derived from 45 patient measurements (hematocrit 38–45%). Geometry tolerance distributions from CMM measurements of 10 pump specimens. All 14 uncertain inputs included in the Monte Carlo UQ ensemble. Input characterization report peer-reviewed. Gradation 4 achieved.",
