      "requiredLevel": 3,
      "achievedLevel": 4,
      "rationale": "Validation experiments conducted using three independently manufactured FDA generic pump specimens (confirmed dimensional conformance via CMM). Each specimen tested in triplicate at each operating point (n=9 per operating point, N=45 total hemolysis measurements). Statistical power analysis confirmed n=9 sufficient to detect a 15% difference in NIH at 80% power (α=0.05). Between-specimen variability (CV=4.2%) and within-specimen variability (CV=2.8%) separately characterized. Gradation 4 achieved, exceeding Gradation 3 requirement.",
